{{Use dmy dates|date=February 2018}} '''List of Hellenistic monetary standards''' includes weight standards used to determine desired weight and size of the produced coinage.
Weights of certain coins, including [[tetradrachm]], [[didrachm]], [[drachm]] and [[hemidrachm]], are given here in [[gram]]s for comparison. Evolution of standards, such as changes in weight, are not reflected in this list.
